Console Drag Race Tree

This program was written for fun to print a simple ascii drag racing light tree
on the console.

It reprints itself every 10 seconds. You can terminate the program by hitting
CTRL+C.

This program requires the ncurses library.

On Ubuntu, you could install it using APT.

sudo apt-get install libncurses5-dev

Compiling:

make

Running:

./drag_race_cli_tree

